# ⚠️ SECURITY GUIDELINES FOR PRODUCTION:

# 1. Generate a strong passphrase:
#    - Minimum 20 characters
#    - Mix of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, special characters
#    - Use a password manager to generate random passphrases

# 2. Store securely:
#    - Use Azure Key Vault for production secrets
#    - Enable Key Vault access policies for your Function App Managed Identity
#    - Never hardcode passphrases in code or configuration files

# 3. Rotate regularly:
#    - Implement passphrase rotation policy (e.g., every 90 days)
#    - Update Key Vault secrets and redeploy applications

